.Dd January 12, 2024
.Dt PMAP_INIT 9
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm pmap_init
.Nd initialize the pmap subsystem
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In sys/param.h
.In vm/vm.h
.In vm/pmap.h
.Ft void
.Fn pmap_init "void"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn pmap_init
function initializes the
.Xr pmap 9
sub-system.
It is called during system initialization by
.Fn vm_mem_init ,
to initialize any structures that the
.Nm
system needs in order to map between physical and virtual memory.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr pmap 9
